<div class="min-h-screen py-8">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto bg-white border border-gray-200 rounded-xl shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl transition-shadow duration-200 p-6">
      <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-3">
        <h1 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-gray-900">Share Your <%= @story_idea.class.model_name.human %></h1>
      </div>

      <div class="">
        This Story Share was created to uplift your voice and experiences as an anchor for your peers, as well as to illustrate to the general public the transformative and healing power of art you witness every day.
        <br><br>
        Thank you for taking the time to fill out the form below. We look forward to reading each and every story about the innovation and transformation of both you and your participants. Please note: minor edits may be made and not all stories will be published to the site, but may still be used in other places.
      </div>

      <div class="border-b border-gray-300 mb-6"></div>

      <div class="space-y-6">
        <div class="mt-4">
          <%= render 'form', story_idea: @story_idea %>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
